    <p class="abstract mathjax">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Abstract</span>:
      <span class="abstract-short has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="math/9909013v3-abstract-short" style="display: inline;">
        An algorithm is given for computing explicit formulas for the generators of relations among the invariant rational functions for vector-valued bilinear forms.
  These formulas have applications in the geometry of Riemannian submanifolds and in CR geometry.
        
      </span>
      <span class="abstract-full has-text-grey-dark mathjax" id="math/9909013v3-abstract-full" style="display: none;">
          An algorithm is given for computing explicit formulas for the generators of relations among the invariant rational functions for vector-valued bilinear forms.
  These formulas have applications in the geometry of Riemannian submanifolds and in CR geometry.
